metadata.name: BORED PEPE #1
metadata.description: The Bored Pepe Vip Club is a collection of 10,000 Bored Pepe NFTs unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Bored Pepe doubles as your Vip Club membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to PEPE LOUNGE, a collaborative graffiti board. Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
